<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,502,621]" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">
Differs from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Baral" authorityYear="2006" baseAuthorityName="Velen." box="[301,565,502,525]" class="Leotiomycetes" family="Hyaloscyphaceae" genus="Roseodiscus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Helotiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="53" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="equisetinus">
<emphasis box="[301,565,502,525]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">Roseodiscus equisetinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in smaller asci and smaller ellipsoid ascospores, and from 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Baral" authorityYear="2006" baseAuthorityName="Sacc." box="[1247,1403,502,525]" class="Leotiomycetes" family="Hyaloscyphaceae" genus="Roseodiscus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Helotiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="53" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="subcarneus">
<emphasis box="[1247,1403,502,525]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">R. subcarneus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in narrower asci and shorter ascospores of a different shape.
</paragraph>
