<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="53" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1814,1956]" box="[198,1015,1814,1840]" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,372,1814,1840]" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">Etymology:—</emphasis>
The specific epithet refers to the locality of the fungus.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,1814,1956]" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,307,1852,1878]" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">Notes:—</emphasis>
The taxonomic position of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="H. D. Zheng &amp; W. Y. Zhuang" authorityYear="2013" box="[649,768,1853,1878]" class="Leotiomycetes" family="Hyaloscyphaceae" genus="Roseodiscus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Helotiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="53" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="sinicus">
<emphasis box="[649,768,1853,1878]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">R. sinicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was further confirmed by the analysis of ITS rDNA sequences (
<figureCitation box="[286,359,1891,1917]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="4.[151,246,1165,1186]" captionTargetBox="[254,1337,159,1139]" captionTargetId="figure-316@4.[244,1351,125,1163]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 4. One of two maximum parsimony trees obtained from ITS rDNA sequences of Roseodiscus sinicus and allied fungi. Bootstrap support values are indicated at the nodes. CI = 0.7324, RI = 0.7480, HI = 0.2676." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5078594" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5078594/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
). The maximum parsimony tree indicated that it is closely related to the 
<typeStatus box="[1217,1267,1891,1917]" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">type</typeStatus>
species of the genus, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Baral" authorityYear="2006" baseAuthorityName="Fr." box="[234,410,1930,1955]" class="Leotiomycetes" family="Hyaloscyphaceae" genus="Roseodiscus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Helotiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="53" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="rhodoleucus">
<emphasis box="[234,410,1930,1955]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">R. rhodoleucus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, with high bootstrap value (100%), rather than any other species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gray" authorityYear="1821" box="[1208,1398,1930,1955]" class="Leotiomycetes" family="Helotiaceae" genus="Hymenoscyphus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Helotiales" pageId="2" pageNumber="53" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1208,1398,1930,1955]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="53">Hymenoscyphus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
